#### **매번 정제->차트 하려니 귀찮으니까 그냥 함수를 만든다** ####

```python
def stackBarChart(feature):
    survived = train_df.loc[train_df["Survived"] == 1][feature].value_counts()
    survived.name = "Survived"
    dead = train_df.loc[train_df["Survived"] == 0][feature].value_counts()
    dead.name = "Dead"
    chart_df = pd.DataFrame([survived,dead])
    chart_df.plot(kind="bar",stacked=True)
```

> 4) Feature Engineering
>
> : 문자열로 된 컬럼값을 숫자로 변경
>
> Text(string) type is hard to machine learning
>
> you have to change apporpriate scale of number
>
> It is better to replace NaN to appropriate value than delete NaN Value. 

```python
# The first thing you have to change is Name Value
# The Name column looks meaningless, but the name's specific keyword can affect the ratio of survival.
train_df["Title"] = train_df["Name"].str.extract("([A-Za-z]+)\.")
train_df["Title"].value_counts()
```

```python
# TItle안에 Mr. Miss, Mrs. others를 각각 0,1,2,3 으로 치환
# 마스크 생성
title_mapping_dict = {"Mr" : 0, "Miss" : 1, "Mrs" : 2, "Master":3, "Dr" : 3, "Rev": 3,"Mlle" : 3, "Major" : 3,"Col": 3, "Mme" : 3, "Countess": 3,"Jonkheer" : 3,"Sir": 3, "Don": 3, "Capt" : 3, "Lady" : 3,"Ms" : 3}
train_df["Title"] = train_df["Title"].map(title_mapping_dict)
```

```python
train_df["Title"].value_counts() # 각 범례의 수 확인
#0    517
#1    182
#2    125
#3     67
# Name: Title, dtype: int64
stackBarChart("Title")
```

> 6) 탑승지역 결측치 처리 및 수치화
>
> 결측치를 S로 대체 -> S에서 사람이 제일 많이탔다(는 빈약한 근거 제시하였음)

```python
train_df["Embarked"] = train_df["Embarked"].fillna("S") # Na를 S 값으로 채움
# 탑승 지역 컬럼 변경하기 S -> 0, Q-> 1, C ->2
embarked_mapping_dict = {"S":0,"Q":1,"C":2}
train_df["Embarked"] = train_df['Embarked'].map(embarked_mapping_dict)
```

> 7) Age 결측치 처리 및 범주화

###### ① 결측치 처리

```python
# 컬럼을 삭제할 수 없고 결측치를 대체해야함
# Title의 호칭을 활용하여 호칭별 평균 나이를 통해 결측치 처리

train_df.groupby("Title")["Age"].mean()
# Title
# 0    32.368090
# 1    21.773973
# 2    35.898148
# 3    20.430161
# Name: Age, dtype: float64
a = train_df[train_df["Title"]==0]["Age"].fillna(train_df.groupby("Title")["Age"].mean()[0])
b = train_df[train_df["Title"]==1]["Age"].fillna(train_df.groupby("Title")["Age"].mean()[1])
c = train_df[train_df["Title"]==2]["Age"].fillna(train_df.groupby("Title")["Age"].mean()[2])
d = train_df[train_df["Title"]==3]["Age"].fillna(train_df.groupby("Title")["Age"].mean()[3])

result_series =  pd.concat([a,b,c,d,]) # a,b,c,d를 합침
train_df["Age"] = result_series.sort_index()
```

② 범주화

```python
# Age에 대해서 Binning 처리
# Binning 처리를 할 때 고려해야 할 사항 ->간격을 어떻게 설정?
# 0~ 20: 0
# 21 ~ 40: 1
# 41~60 : 2
# 60초과: 3

train_df.loc[train_df["Age"] <= 20, "Age"] = 0
train_df.loc[(train_df["Age"] > 20) & (train_df["Age"] <= 40), "Age"]= 1
train_df.loc[(train_df["Age"] > 40) & (train_df["Age"] <= 60), "Age" ]= 2
train_df.loc[train_df["Age"] > 60, "Age"] = 3
stackBarChart("Age")
```
